(firstQuint)A Study to Assess Efficacy and Safety of RT001 in Subjects With Infantile Neuroaxonal Dystrophy.

 This is a single arm open-label study with a structured observation of INAD patients treated with RT001.

 Enrolled subjects will undergo observation and testing to determine the effect of RT001 treatment.

 Fifteen eligible subjects will be treated with RT001 for long-term evaluation of efficacy, safety, tolerability, and pharmacokinetics.

